snippet.title: 9Lives Arena (9LA) Closed Alpha 0.4 Gameplay Footage
snippet.description:
9Lives Arena (9LA) is a competitive online RPG for PC and consoles that also incorporates blockchain technology (Enjin Coin) to give players true item ownership. 
Pre-order alpha access via our shop online https://www.9livesarena.com 

Join us on: 
https://t.me/NineLivesArena
https://discordapp.com/invite/weqNqKJ
https://twitter.com/9livesarena
https://instragram.com/9livesarena
